criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Overweight and obesity grade I, according to WHO criteria (1998).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Normal weight, obesity> grade I;

          -  Use of appetite-enhancing medications such as glucocorticoids, tricyclic
             antidepressants, antipsychotics, mood modulators and anticonvulsants, or reduce body
             weight , such as anorexigenics, and antidiabetics that can modify body weight;

          -  In follow-up or nutritional intervention already established and;

          -  Refusal to sign the informed consent form.
